About Akar Salim

Visionary Behind AkarCert

Akar Salim is a pioneering technologist with a deep passion for digital security and decentralized solutions. With a background in blockchain and AI, Akar founded AkarCert to revolutionize how we create, manage, and verify digital certificates. His mission is to empower individuals and organizations with secure, transparent, and instantly verifiable credentials.

Our Mission & Milestones

2020: Inception & Research

Extensive research into blockchain technology and its application to digital document verification.

2021: Prototype Development

Development of the initial AkarCert platform prototype, focusing on core generation and verification.

2022: AI Integration

Successfully integrated advanced AI algorithms for smart certificate generation and customization.

2023: Marketplace Launch

Public launch of the AkarCert marketplace, connecting creators and buyers globally.

2024: Global Expansion & API

Expanding to new markets and releasing API for third-party integrations.
